{"word":"H1235 - בֶּקַע - beqaʻ - beh'-kah - Bekah","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">בֶּקַע</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>beqaʻ"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>beh'-kah"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Bekah"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"அரைச்சேக்கல், பெக்கா - ஆண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"half, part also called \"shekel of the sanctuary\" or \"holy shekel\" half a shekel"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Masculine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (ஆண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/H1234 - בָּקַע - bâqaʻ - baw-kah'/1234\">H1234</a>; a <i>section</i> (half) of a shekel, that is, a <i>beka</i> (a weight and a coin): - bekah, half a shekel."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1233 - בְּקִיעַ - bᵉqîyaʻ - bek-ee'-ah/1233\">H1233</a>, <a href=\"#/H1234 - בָּקַע - bâqaʻ - baw-kah'/1234\">H1234</a>, <a href=\"#/H1235 - בֶּקַע - beqaʻ - beh'-kah/1235\">H1235</a>, <a href=\"#/H1237 - בִּקְעָה - biqʻâh - bik-aw'/1237\">H1237</a>"}]}